# web/.env.local.example
#
# Server-only environment for the Customer 360 demo. Copy to `web/.env.local` for
# `next dev` (gitignored), and set the SAME five vars as Vercel Project Environment
# Variables (Production + Preview) for the deploy.
#
# SECURITY (T-06-11 / T-06-12): these are ALL server-only secrets. NONE may carry a
# `NEXT_PUBLIC_` prefix — that would bundle them into the browser. The Node-runtime
# /api/ask route + the arangojs keep-alive singleton read them from process.env
# server-side ONLY. `.env.local` / `.env` are gitignored — never commit real values.

# --- ArangoDB (the shared prod ArangoGraph cluster; dedicated customer360 DB) ---
# Values from the local .env (see MEMORY: arango-connection).
ARANGO_ENDPOINT=
ARANGO_USERNAME=
ARANGO_PASSWORD=
ARANGO_DATABASE=

# --- OpenAI (embeddings + the planner/answerer model; D-06) ---
OPENAI_API_KEY=
